nodes.text: Drew Z. Greenberg is a writer for the Star Wars: The Clone Wars TV series. His work includes the season one episodes "The Hidden Enemy" and "Hostage Crisis," as well as the season two episodes, "Children of the Force," "Senate Spy," "Landing at Point Rain," "Weapons Factory," "Legacy of Terror," "Brain Invaders," "Grievous Intrigue," "The Deserter," "Lightsaber Lost," "The Mandalore Plot," "Duchess of Mandalore", and "Cat and Mouse."
